title: Leading influencers on Instagram in Sweden 2017 , by followers
summary: This is a bar chart. It shows Instagram followers in millions for 10 number of Months.
The Instagram followers in millions is appeared to be the highest at Month Anna Nyström (annanystrom) and lowest at Month TrainForFitspo (trainforfitspo).
The maximum Month Anna Nyström (annanystrom) has got 9.61 times higher Instagram followers in millions than the minimum Month TrainForFitspo (trainforfitspo).
